snippet.description:

Watch match highlights from the Day 2 of the Rothesay Test between England and India at Headingley, Leeds.

This is the official channel of the ECB. Watch all the latest videos from the England Cricket teams and England and Wales Cricket Board, including highlights, interviews and features getting you closer to the England teams and county players.

Subscribe for more: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

Featuring video from the England cricket teams, Vitality Blast, County Championship, Metro Bank One-Day Cup and more.

hi.title: पोप और पंत ने शतक बनाए! | हाइलाइट्स - इंग्लैंड बनाम भारत दिन 2 | रोथेसे टेस्ट 2025
hi.description:
ecb.co.uk पर जाकर We Are England Cricket Supporters से निःशुल्क जुड़ें और टिकटों तथा अन्य बहुत सी चीज़ों तक प्राथमिकता प्राप्त करें!

हेडिंग्ले, लीड्स में इंग्लैंड और भारत के बीच रोथेसे टेस्ट के दूसरे दिन के मैच हाइलाइट्स देखें।

यह ECB का आधिकारिक चैनल है। इंग्लैंड क्रिकेट टीमों और इंग्लैंड और वेल्स क्रिकेट बोर्ड के सभी नवीनतम वीडियो देखें, जिसमें हाइलाइट्स, साक्षात्कार और इंग्लैंड टीमों और काउंटी खिलाड़ियों के बारे में आपको और करीब लाने वाली विशेषताएँ शामिल हैं।

अधिक जानकारी के लिए सदस्यता लें: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

इंग्लैंड क्रिकेट टीमों, विटैलिटी ब्लास्ट, काउंटी चैम्पियनशिप, मेट्रो बैंक वन-डे कप और बहुत कुछ के वीडियो शामिल हैं।

ko.description:

더 많은 정보를 원하시면 구독하세요: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

잉글랜드 크리켓 팀, 바이탈리티 블라스트, 카운티 챔피언십, 메트로 뱅크 원데이 컵 등의 영상을 제공합니다.

కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ అనుకోని రీతిలో ఈ లోకాన్ని విడిచిన విషాదవార్తను తెలియజేయడం చాలా బాధాకరం. కోచ్ వాల్ అందరి హృదయాలను తాకిన మానవత్వం, దయామయమైన వ్యక్తిత్వం కలిగిన అసాధారణ వ్యక్తి.

ఈ విషాదకర సంఘటన అనంతరం, ఈ వీడియోను పంచుకోవాలా వద్దా అనే విషయంలో కోచ్ వాల్ కుటుంబాన్ని సంప్రదించాం. వారి తెలివైన మరియు పరిపక్వమైన స్పందనలో, ""టైలర్ ఆశాభావం మరియు సానుకూలతను ప్రపంచానికి చేరవేయాలనే తన ఆకాంక్ష ఈ సమయంలో కూడా కొనసాగాలి"" అని చెప్పారు.

ఈ కష్ట సమయంలో, మీరు కోచ్ వాల్ యొక్క జ్ఞాపకాన్ని గౌరవించి, ఆయన కుటుంబానికి గౌరవంగా ప్రైవసీని కల్పించమని మనవి చేస్తున్నాము.

కోచ్ టైలర్ వాల్ యొక్క సానుభూతి మరియు ప్రోత్సాహ పాఠాలు ఆయన గురించి తెలిసిన అందరి హృదయాల్లో ఎప్పటికీ నిలిచి ఉంటాయి.

మీరు కలలుగంటున్న వ్యాపారాన్ని ప్రారంభించండి! ఇప్పుడే https://www.Shopify.com/MrBeast  ను సందర్శించి మీ ట్రయల్ ప్రారంభించండి.

ਬਹੁਤ ਹੀ ਦੁਖ ਭਰੀ ਸੂਚਨਾ ਦੇ ਨਾਲ ਅਸੀਂ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸ ਰਹੇ ਹਾਂ ਕਿ ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਹੁਣ ਸਾਡੇ ਵਿਚ ਨਹੀਂ ਰਹੇ। ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਇਕ ਬੇਮਿਸਾਲ ਇਨਸਾਨ ਸਨ, ਜਿਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਦਇਆਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਖੁਸ਼ਮਿਜਾਜ਼ੀ ਨੇ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਮਿਲਣ ਵਾਲੇ ਹਰ ਵਿਅਕਤੀ ਦੇ ਦਿਲ ਨੂੰ ਛੋਹ ਲਿਆ।
ਉਹਨਾਂ ਦੇ ਅਚਾਨਕ ਵਿਛੋੜੇ ਨੇ ਸਾਡੇ ਦਿਲਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਗਮੀ ਨਾਲ ਭਰ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ।

ਇਸ ਦੁਖਦਾਈ ਘੜੀ 'ਚ, ਅਸੀਂ ਕੋਚ ਵਾਲ ਦੇ ਪਰਿਵਾਰ ਨਾਲ ਸੰਪਰਕ ਕੀਤਾ
ਜਿਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਨੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਸਹਿਣਸ਼ੀਲਤਾ ਅਤੇ ਸਿਆਣਪ ਨਾਲ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਦੱਸਿਆ ਕਿ
ਟਾਈਲਰ ਚਾਹੁੰਦੇ ਸਨ ਕਿ ਉਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਦੀ ਆਸ ਅਤੇ ਸਕਾਰਾਤਮਕਤਾ ਭਰੀ ਸੋਚ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਤੱਕ ਪਹੁੰਚਦੀ ਰਹੇ, ਭਾਵੇਂ ਉਹ ਸਾਢੇ ਨਾਮ ਹੋਣ ਜਾਂ ਨਾ ਹੋਣ।

ਕੋਚ ਟਾਈਲਰ ਵਾਲ ਦੀ ਹੌਂਸਲੇ ਅਤੇ ਦਿਲਾਸੇ ਭਰੀ ਵਿਰਾਸਤ

**கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் அன்பான நினைவாக**

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் எதிர்பாராத மறைவுச் செய்தியை ஆழ்ந்த துக்கத்துடன் பகிர்ந்துகொள்கிறோம். கோச் வால் ஒரு அற்புதமான மனிதர், அவரது கருணையும் உண்மையான மனப்பான்மையும் அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரையும் கவர்ந்தது. அவரது இழப்பு எங்கள் இதயங்களை துயரத்தால் கனக்கச் செய்துள்ளது.

இந்தத் துயரச் செய்தியைத் தொடர்ந்து, இந்த வீடியோவை வெளியிட வேண்டுமா என்று கோச் வால் குடும்பத்தினரை அணுகினோம். அவர்கள், தங்கள் ஞானத்தோடும் பெருந்தன்மையோடும், டைலர் இல்லாத நிலையிலும் அவரது நம்பிக்கை மற்றும் நேர்மறையான செய்தி மற்றவர்களைச் சென்றடைய வேண்டும் என்று விரும்பியிருப்பார் எனத் தெரிவித்தனர்.

இந்தக் கடினமான நேரத்தில் கோச் வால் அவர்களின் நினைவைப் போற்றுமாறும், அவரது குடும்பத்தினரின் தனிப்பட்ட உரிமையை மதிக்குமாறும் தாழ்மையுடன் கேட்டுக்கொள்கிறோம்.

கோச் டைலர் வால் அவர்களின் இரக்கமும் ஊக்கமும் நிறைந்த மரபு, அவரை அறிந்த அனைவரின் இதயங்களிலும் நிலைத்திருக்கும்.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

Feel the rhythm take over with Dil Thaam Ke — the ultimate dance Song from Maalik! Starring Rajkummar Rao and Huma Qureshi, this high-energy track features electrifying music by Sachin-Jigar, soulful vocals by Rashmeet Kaur & Rana Majumdar, and powerful lyrics penned by Amitabh Bhattacharya.

In Cinemas 11th July 2025

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Official. Subscribe on the link below.
http://youtube.com/tipsofficial

Song Details : 
Music - Sachin - Jigar
Singer: Rashmeet Kaur, Rana Majumdar
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya 
Music Production Head - Romil Ved
Programmed & Arranged :- Abhishek Singh (White Noise Collectives) 
Recording Engineer : Swar Mehta & Susmeet Rewaskar (White Noise Collectives)
Mixed & Mastered : Eric Pillai 
Assistant Mix Engineer : Michael Edwin Pillai

Movie Details : 
Banner: Tips Films Ltd. & Northern Lights Films
Directed By Pulkit
Produced By Kumar Taurani & Jay Shewakramani
Cast: Rajkummar Rao, Prosenjit Chatterjee, Manushi Chhillar, Medha Shankr, Huma Qureshi, Swanand Kirkire 
Director Of Photography: Anuj Rakesh Dhawan
Written By Jyotsana Nath & Pulkit

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4429 - Bhide ko Dikhi Bhootni?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. 

Are you ready for the challenge? 
Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  
#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Falguni Pathak - Meri Chunar Udd Udd Jaye (Official Lyric Video) | Romantic Song
snippet.description:
Experience the magic of one of the most loved Indian pop songs of all time – "Meri Chunar Udd Udd Jaye" by the queen of dandiya, Falguni Pathak!

This iconic track is more than just music; it's a journey through emotions, love, and the magic of Falguni Pathak's enchanting voice. 🌠

Join us in celebrating the everlasting charm of this song as it transcends time, taking you on a melodic voyage that will touch your heart and uplift your spirits. 🎤

snippet.title: Sitaare Zameen Par Movie REVIEW | Suraj Kumar
snippet.description:
SITAARE ZAMEEN PAR Review | Aamir Khan & Genelia Return with an Emotional Ride? 

Aamir Khan is back — this time with Sitaare Zameen Par, alongside Genelia D’Souza in a heartfelt drama that explores learning disabilities, redemption, and second chances.
But does the film live up to the emotional weight of Taare Zameen Par or does it fall into the trap of forced sentimentality?

In this review, I dive into the performances, storytelling, emotional depth, and how the film handles sensitive themes.
Is this a genuine comeback or just nostalgia bait? Let’s break it all down.

snippet.title: GAANJI - Official Music Video | Chandan Shetty | Folk x Fusion
snippet.description:
From North Karnataka to the World: A Folk Song Reimagined Through Dance. Having zero expectations and a full heart, I present to you this experimental music video — a piece of art born from a deeply personal journey.

I composed this song nine years ago, inspired by a beloved folk rhyme from North Karnataka. Over time, its melody stayed close to me, quietly asking to be brought to life in a new form.

The visual inspiration comes from a range of minimalistic music videos, especially those shot on white-screen backgrounds (like ‘Sorry’ from Justin Bieber). I finally started working on the video in 2023, and just two months ago, we brought it to life.

We held virtual auditions across India, and with the brilliant support of choreographers Praveen Veigas,  Pushpa, and Muskan, we selected 10 incredible dancers who brought their energy and magic to this performance.

This project would not have been possible without the dedication and brilliance of a phenomenal team:
        •        Co-Producer: Greeshma Gowda
        •        DOP: Suhas Amin
        •        Editor & VFX: Dheeraj Poojary
        •        Programming, Mixing & Mastering: Agastya Raag
        •       Dancers: Alina Khan, Yukta, Muskan, Chaitanya, Payal, Jaquline, Sana, Shivani, Sneha.
        •       Chorus: Mahalakshmi, Harismaran . A, Harshit N.U, Siri B.S, Prerana Navalgi, Nikisha H.A, Sana .S, Meghana Saishree, Shivani .S, Kshama .D Raj, Sanchita Vinay, M. Madhumitha, Dhriti Vishwanath, Isha .V, Omkar Kumble, Ghanashyam G.R, Tanav .S, Arav G.A, Ruchitha .V, Ridhima .K, Pranathi .V, Panvi N.U.
        •      Poster Design : Ankith Anil 
        •      Digitally Distributed by A3 Labels
        •      Digital Promotions: Digital Magnet Media - Dhanu Krishnaa


To all the technicians and artists involved — your work has been outstanding, and I deeply appreciate each one of you.

This video is directed by Chandan Shetty, and represents not just a song, but a dream nurtured over time.

I truly hope you connect with it, feel the spirit behind it, and show it some love.

I composed this song nine years ago, inspired by a beloved folk rhyme from North Karnataka. Over time, its melody stayed close to me, quietly asking to be brought to life in a new form.

The visual inspiration comes from a range of minimalistic music videos, especially those shot on white-screen backgrounds (like ‘Sorry’ from Justin Bieber). I finally started working on the video in 2023, and just two months ago, we brought it to life.

We held virtual auditions across India, and with the brilliant support of choreographers Praveen Veigas,  Pushpa, and Muskan, we selected 10 incredible dancers who brought their energy and magic to this performance.

This project would not have been possible without the dedication and brilliance of a phenomenal team:
        •        Co-Producer: Greeshma Gowda
        •        DOP: Suhas Amin
        •        Editor & VFX: Dheeraj Poojary
        •        Programming, Mixing & Mastering: Agastya Raag
        •       Dancers: Alina Khan, Yukta, Muskan, Chaitanya, Payal, Jaquline, Sana, Shivani, Sneha.
        •       Chorus: Mahalakshmi, Harismaran . A, Harshit N.U, Siri B.S, Prerana Navalgi, Nikisha H.A, Sana .S, Meghana Saishree, Shivani .S, Kshama .D Raj, Sanchita Vinay, M. Madhumitha, Dhriti Vishwanath, Isha .V, Omkar Kumble, Ghanashyam G.R, Tanav .S, Arav G.A, Ruchitha .V, Ridhima .K, Pranathi .V, Panvi N.U.
        •      Poster Design : Ankith Anil 
        •      Digitally Distributed by A3 Labels
        •      Digital Promotions: Digital Magnet Media - Dhanu Krishnaa


To all the technicians and artists involved — your work has been outstanding, and I deeply appreciate each one of you.

This video is directed by Chandan Shetty, and represents not just a song, but a dream nurtured over time.

I truly hope you connect with it, feel the spirit behind it, and show it some love.

➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken

Daquavis: ​⁠@DaquavisMC 


We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is one hunter and $100,000 is on the line.

This is the third and final duel in our $100,000 challenge. The tiebreaker. 

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.16 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while Daquavis tries to stop me. It's a race, and it's super intense, so much is on the line.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftManhunt

हमने इस सीरीज को Minecraft Manhunt नाम देने का फैसला किया। यह वीडियो इसका एक अलग संस्करण है, जिसमें एक शिकारी है और $100,000 दांव पर है।

यह हमारी $100,000 चुनौती में तीसरा और अंतिम द्वंद्व है। टाईब्रेकर।

यह एक नया Minecraft है, लेकिन, 1.16 चुनौती जिसे हमने आजमाने का फैसला किया है। मैं गेम को जीतने की कोशिश करता हूं, जबकि दक्वाविस मुझे रोकने की कोशिश करता है। यह एक दौड़ है, और यह बहुत तीव्र है, बहुत कुछ दांव पर लगा है।

Minecraft नहीं, बल्कि Water Rises या Minecraft नहीं, बल्कि Lava Rises, या कोई और चुनौती नहीं बल्कि ऐसी ही चुनौती। यह Minecraft का एक स्पीड रन / स्पीड रनर है जो एक हत्यारे / हत्यारे के खिलाफ है

#MinecraftManhunt

ja.title: マインクラフト スピードランナー VS 10万ドルの賞金稼ぎ
ja.description:
Daquavis VS Dreamの最終決戦。これは本当に最高でした。

$7,000メダルコンテストへの参加はこちら：https://pages.medal.tv/dream

Daquavis: ​⁠@DaquavisMC

このシリーズは「Minecraft Manhunt」と名付けることにしました。この動画は、ハンターが1人で賞金10万ドルを賭けた、少し変わったバージョンです。

これは、10万ドルチャレンジの3回目にして最後の決闘です。タイブレーカーです。

これは、Minecraftの新しいバージョンですが、バージョン1.16で挑戦することにしました。私はゲームをクリアしようとしますが、Daquavisはそれを阻止しようとします。レースです。しかも超激戦で、多くのものが賭けられています。

Minecraftではなく、Water Rises、Minecraftではなく、Lava Rises、あるいはその他、そういった類のチャレンジではありません。これは、殺人鬼／暗殺者と戦うMinecraftのスピードラン／スピードランナーです。

#MinecraftManhunt

Decidimos chamar esta série de Minecraft Manhunt. Este vídeo é uma versão diferente, onde há um caçador e US$ 100.000 estão em jogo.

Este é o terceiro e último duelo do nosso desafio de US$ 100.000. O desempate.

Este é um novo desafio do Minecraft, mas da versão 1.16, que decidimos tentar. Eu tento terminar o jogo, enquanto Daquavis tenta me impedir. É uma corrida superintensa, com muita coisa em jogo.

Não é Minecraft, mas Water Rises, ou Minecraft, mas Lava Rises, ou qualquer outro desafio parecido. Esta é uma corrida rápida de Minecraft contra um assassino.

#MinecraftManhunt

ko.title: 마인크래프트 스피드러너 vs 10만 달러 현상금 사냥꾼
ko.description:
다콰비스 VS 드림 결승전. 정말 최고였어요!

$7,000 메달 경연 대회 참가 신청: https://pages.medal.tv/dream

➽ 인스타그램 - @dreamwastaken
➽ 스냅챗 - @dreampublic

상품: https://www.dreams.is

이 시리즈의 이름을 '마인크래프트 맨헌트'로 정했습니다. 이 영상은 마인크래프트 맨헌트의 다른 버전인데, 한 명의 헌터가 10만 달러를 걸고 싸우는 내용입니다.

$10만 챌린지의 세 번째이자 마지막 결투입니다. 승패를 가르는 경기입니다.

새로운 마인크래프트 버전 1.16 챌린지인데, 이번에 도전해 보기로 했습니다. 저는 게임에서 이기기 위해 노력하는 반면, 다콰비스는 저를 막으려 합니다. 마치 경주처럼 치열하고, 정말 많은 것이 걸려 있습니다.

마인크래프트는 아니지만, 워터 라이즈(Water Rises)나 마인크래프트지만 라바 라이즈(Lava Rises) 같은 챌린지 말고 다른 것도 괜찮습니다. 이건 킬러/암살자를 상대로 하는 마인크래프트 스피드런/스피드러너 게임입니다.

snippet.title: Back to Back Comedy Scenes 😍🤣| Kick | Ravi Teja | Brahmanandam | Ilena | Ali | Telugu Comedy Scene
snippet.description:
Kick is a 2009 Indian Telugu-language action comedy film directed by Surender Reddy from a story by Vakkantham Vamsi. The film stars Ravi Teja, Ileana, and Shaam while Brahmanandam plays a supporting role. 

నైనా(ఇలియానా)కి పోలీస్ ఆఫీసర్ కళ్యాణ కృష్ణ(శ్యామ్)కి పెళ్ళి చూపులలో తన ప్రేమ కథని శ్యామ్ కి చెప్తుంది. ఆ కథలో కళ్యాణ్ (రవితేజ) చిన్నప్పటి నుంచీ కిక్..కిక్ అంటూ కలవరిస్తూంటాడు. అందుకుతగ్గట్లుగానే కిక్ ఇవ్వని ఏ పనీ చెయ్యడు...కిక్కు ఇస్తుందంటే ఎటువంటి పని చెయ్యటానికైనా వెనకాడడు..అంతేగాక కిక్ తగ్గిపోతే ఆ పనిలో కొనసాగటానికి ఇష్టపడడు. దాంతో ఏ ఉద్యోగంలోనూ వారం మించి పనిచేయడు. అలాంటి అతని విచిత్ర జీవితంలోకి ప్రతీది పెపఫెక్ట్ గా ఉండాలనుకునే ఇలియానా ప్రవేశిస్తుంది. అతని ఏటిట్యూడ్ చూసి మొదట ఆమె కసురుకున్నా తర్వాత ప్రేమలో పడుతుంది. పడిందే తడువుగా అతన్ని ఏదన్నా ఉద్యోగంలో చేరి సెటిల్ అవ్వమంటుంది.

snippet.title: बचपन का प्यार ढूंढने इंडिया लौटी करीना - Kareena & Tusshar Kapoor ज़बरदस्त सीन - Jeena Sirf Mere Liye
snippet.description:
► Click here to Subscribe the channel : https://bit.ly/3HS054l 

बचपन का प्यार ढूंढने इंडिया लौटी करीना - ज़बरदस्त सीन - Kareena Kapoor, Tusshar Kapoor, Mallika Sherawat - Jeena Sirf Mere Liye 2002 - Blockbuster Movie - Superhit 

The story revolves around Karan and Pooja, two young friends who meet at a picturesque hill station every summer. However, fate intervenes when Pooja’s affluent family relocates, leading to their estrangement. As they
mature, both characters harbour memories of their bond, with Pooja finding solace in her writing and Karan unintentionally caught in a romantic misunderstanding with Seema, played by Mallika Sherawat. A culmination of
misunderstandings, familial pressures, and emotional realisations eventually lead them back to each other, imploring viewers to reflect on the complexities of love and connection.

◾ Film : Jeena Sirf Merre Liye 2002 (जीना सिर्फ मेरे लिये)
◾ Director :- Talat Jani (तलत जानी)
◾ Cast: - Kareena Kapoor (करीना कपूर), Tusshar Kapoor (तुषार कपूर), Kader Khan (कादर खान), Mallika Sherawat (मल्लिका शेरावत), Alok Nath (आलोक नाथ), Himani Shivpuri (हिमानी शिवपुरी), Vijayendra Ghatge
◾ Genre:- Romantic Drama रोमांटिक ड्रामा
◾ Language:- Hindi

hi.title: KL Rahul और Ben Stokes की सबसे कठिन बैटिंग चुनौती!
hi.description:
बेन स्टोक्स और के.एल. राहुल मिलकर क्रिकेट की अब तक की सबसे चुनौतीपूर्ण बैटिंग चैलेंज का सामना करने वाले हैं! 

आने वाली टेस्ट सीरीज़ से पहले, दोनों को अपनी-अपनी व्यक्तिगत क्रिकेट परीक्षाओं से गुजरना होगा — जहाँ उनकी सटीकता और ताकत की असली परख होगी। 

इसके बाद ही वे एक साथ मिलकर तेज़ तर्रार बॉलिंग मशीनों और तेजी से हिलते लक्ष्यों के खिलाफ एक रोमांचक "बॉस बैटल" में उतरेंगे।

kn.title: ದಿ ಅಲ್ಟಿಮೇಟ್ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಬ್ಯಾಟಿಂಗ್ ಚಾಲೆಂಜ್ (KL Rahul ಮತ್ತು Ben Stokes)
kn.description:
KL Rahul ಮತ್ತು Ben Stokes ಅಂತಿಮ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಬ್ಯಾಟಿಂಗ್ ಸವಾಲನ್ನು ಎದುರಿಸಲು ಒಗ್ಗೂಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದಾರೆ! 


ಟೆಸ್ಟ್ ಸರಣಿಗೆ ಮೊದಲು, ಅವರು ಪ್ರತ್ಯೇಕವಾಗಿ ತಮ್ಮ ಶಕ್ತಿ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಖರತೆಯನ್ನು ಪರೀಕ್ಷಿಸುವ ವೈಯಕ್ತಿಕ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಸವಾಲುಗಳನ್ನು ಜಯಿಸಬೇಕು. 

 

ಈ ನಂತರ, ಅವರು ಸೇರಿ ಟ್ರಿಕ್ಕಿ ಬೌಲಿಂಗ್

snippet.title: Ep 4430 - PRECAP! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:
Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi

Everyone in the colony is set to enjoy their three-day retreat at the bungalow. But could Taarak’s boss be right about the place being haunted?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: सूजी मूंगदाल फरा नाश्ते के लिए परफेक्ट स्वाद सेहत सादगी नो फ्राई नो झंझट । Steamed Sooji Fara recipe
snippet.description:
तला-भुना छोड़िए,  खाइए ये स्टीम्ड और हेल्दी फरे, बिना झंझट वाला पौष्टिक नाश्ता,पारंपरिक स्वाद, बनाने में एकदम आसान, Sooji Fara Recipe – A Nutritious Start to Your Day,Low-Oil Breakfast – Sooji Fara with Protein-Rich Stuffing
#fara #breakfast #nashtha

Ingredients for Suji Moong Dal Fare
नमक - Salt - 3/4 tsp
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सूजी - Semolina - 1 cup (180 grams)

For Stuffing
मूंग धुली दाल - Moong dhuli dal - 1/2 cup (100 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1/2 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च पाउडर - Red chilli powder - 1/4 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/4 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp, crushed
हींग - Asafoetida - 1/2 pinch
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1-2 tbsp


For Frying
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/4 tsp
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves 
तिल - Sesame - 1/2 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli 
नमक - Salt

snippet.title: England vs India 1st Test: ആദ്യ ദിനം ജയ്സ്വാളിൻ്റെയും ഗില്ലിൻ്റെയും വിളയാട്ടം
snippet.description:
ഇംഗ്ലീഷ് പേസിന് മുന്നിൽ കോട്ട കെട്ടിയും ആക്രമിച്ചു ജയ്സ്വാൾ ബാറ്റ് വീശിയതോടെ ഒരു ഘട്ടത്തിൽ ബാക് ഫുട്ടിലായ ഇന്ത്യയെ ടോപ്പ് ഗിയറിൽ എത്തിച്ചത്. 42 റൺസെടുത്ത കെഎൽ രാഹുൽ കൂടാരം കയറുമ്പോൾ ഇന്ത്യ ഭേദപ്പെട്ട നിലയിലേക്കുള്ള യാത്ര ആരംഭിച്ചിരുന്നു. രാഹുലിനെ ബ്രൈഡൻ കാഴ്സിന്റെ പന്തിൽ ജോ റൂട്ട് ക്യാച്ചെടുത്തു പുറത്താക്കുകയായിരുന്നു. എന്നാൽ മൂന്നാമനായി എത്തിയ സായ് സുദർശൻ റണ്ണൊന്നുമെടുക്കാതെ കൂടാരം കയറിയതോടെയാണ് ഇന്ത്യ ബാക് ഫുട്ടിലായത്.

ഇംഗ്ലീഷ് പേസിന് മുന്നിൽ കോട്ട കെട്ടിയും ആക്രമിച്ചു ജയ്സ്വാൾ ബാറ്റ് വീശിയതോടെ ഒരു ഘട്ടത്തിൽ ബാക് ഫുട്ടിലായ ഇന്ത്യയെ ടോപ്പ് ഗിയറിൽ എത്തിച്ചത്. 42 റൺസെടുത്ത കെഎൽ രാഹുൽ കൂടാരം കയറുമ്പോൾ ഇന്ത്യ ഭേദപ്പെട്ട നിലയിലേക്കുള്ള യാത്ര ആരംഭിച്ചിരുന്നു. രാഹുലിനെ ബ്രൈഡൻ കാഴ്സിന്റെ പന്തിൽ ജോ റൂട്ട് ക്യാച്ചെടുത്തു പുറത്താക്കുകയായിരുന്നു. എന്നാൽ മൂന്നാമനായി എത്തിയ സായ് സുദർശൻ റണ്ണൊന്നുമെടുക്കാതെ കൂടാരം കയറിയതോടെയാണ് ഇന്ത്യ ബാക് ഫുട്ടിലായത്.

Presenting Public review of Kuberaa movie. Kuberaa public review is taken from Bangalore FDFS.

Kuberaa is an 2025 Indian social thriller film directed and co-written by Sekhar Kammula. Produced by Suniel Narang and Puskur Rammohan Rao of Amigos Creations, it is simultaneously shot in Telugu, Tamil and Hindi. The film stars Dhanush, Nagarjuna, Rashmika Mandanna, Jim Sarbh and Dalip Tahil. The film has music composed by Devi Sri Prasad, cinematography by Niketh Bommireddy, editing by Karthika Srinivas and production design by Thota Tharani.

Kuberaa released worldwide from today.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: The Lavari Show EP 51 | Ft. Bhavya Gandhi | Pranks Lavari | The Comedy Factory
snippet.description:
Special Guest - Bhavya Gandhi 

Join us as we chat with Bhavya Gandhi, best known as Tapu from the iconic TV sitcom Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah (2008–2017), a role that made him a household name. After exiting the show, he transitioned to Gujarati cinema, starring in hit films like Pappa Tamne Nahi Samjaay, Bau Na Vichar, Kehvatlal Parivar, and the latest Ajab Raat Ni Gajab Vaat. He also made a Bollywood debut in Striker and appeared in Hindi TV and short films like Shaadi Ke Siyape and Pushpa Impossible. Hailing from a Gujarati Jain family and holding a B.Com from Mumbai University, Bhavya brings a unique cultural and educational perspective to our conversation. In this episode, we explore his journey from child star to regional cinema lead, his passion for music and direction, and what’s next on his creative horizon. 



Artists - 
Manan Desai, Om Bhatt, Deep Vaidya & Chirayu Mistry

snippet.title: Panchayat Season 4 - Official Trailer | Premieres 24th June on @PrimeVideoIN
snippet.description:
Team Manju Devi Vs Team Kranti Devi ka ho chuka hai aagaaz! Phulera mein shuru ho chuka hai election - Manju Devi ya Kranti Devi, kiska hoga selection!

Official Release Date June 24, 2025 on Prime Video.

A TVF Creation
Created by: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Chandan Kumar
Directed by: Akshat Vijaywargiya, Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by: Chandan Kumar
Executive Producers: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey

About:
Amidst the much-awaited village panchayat elections, Pradhan’s and Bhushan’s camps battle tooth and nail to maintain the upper hand. The future of everyone, including Abhishek, hangs in the balance.
